<p>A video shared on Twitter appeared to show protesters hurling a Motolov cocktails towards police officers in Portland </p>

<p>The grand jury indicted one Louisville officer in connection to the March 13 killing, but for shooting into a home next to Taylor's that had people in it. </p>

<p>No charges were brought against the two officers who fired their weapon at Taylor, in her home. </p>

<p>Prosecutors said they were justified in using force to protect themselves after they were shot at.</p>

<p>Taylor, an emergency medical worker, was shot multiple times by white officers who entered her home on a no-knock warrant during a narcotics investigation. </p>

